              "text": "Emotional Design for Creativity",
              "spans": []
            },
            {
              "type": "paragraph",
              "text": "The Emovation Lab was designed as a first-of-its-kind hub for emotional innovation in Sharjah’s Technology and Innovation Park. Created as a space where invention begins with emotion, it offered a multi-sensory environment for students, researchers, and creators to imagine, develop, and showcase new ideas.",
              "spans": []
            }
          ]
